{"tid":861382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乙明邨26歲男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-10-14T05:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:19:36.000Z","uid":70367,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e61aae82616b24256e1ca0d538df51dfb84aa4eb","tid":861382,"uid":70367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/134709_c49054724dbe0448bd258e57dd29ee40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F134709_c49054724dbe0448bd258e57dd29ee40.jpg&h=ab3e45f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田乙明邨明耀樓，凌晨1時16分，一名姓翁26歲男子從高處墮下，倒臥後門對開地下，保安員發現報警。救護員接報到場，證實已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，死者與家人同住上址，患有抑鬱症，相信從樓梯位置墮下。警方沒有撿獲遺書，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/134819_e03bbf6db4607be10757b4516fcb5bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F134819_e03bbf6db4607be10757b4516fcb5bff.jpg&h=e91c069a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/134823_62a933eec7cbbb3c46db70865c02ed3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F134823_62a933eec7cbbb3c46db70865c02ed3d.jpg&h=a8738d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181014/58792306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58792306&d=gVFI0nuS7Zb4WW4BWPLu80%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=31b1ddfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F